      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Sun</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>This guy </l>
          <l>Knows what he's talking about </l>
          <l>He blows away my devil's doubt </l>
          <l>I'm in too deep </l>
          <l>I walk asleep </l>
          <l>He guides me north </l>
          <l>When I'm going south </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>This guy </l>
          <l>Taught me what I am about </l>
          <l>Broke the walls and left me to watch </l>
          <l>This movie scene I'm starring in </l>
          <l>Won't begin I see the end </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Though I know I'll get hurt </l>
          <l>I wish he'd stay </l>
          <l>Though I know I'll be better </l>
          <l>Without him I can't release </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>You make sense </l>
          <l>It's obvious </l>
          <l>It's underneath my bones </l>
          <l>I find myself </l>
          <l>Where no one else </l>
          <l>Is reaching for the sun </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>At night </l>
          <l>He knows what I'm talking about </l>
          <l>When I'm lost in a beautiful gown </l>
          <l>Like a child I want him know </l>
          <l>These lonely nights he's not around </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>Though I know I'll get hurt </l>
